{"tid":1491434,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴打可以整個元朗 721 apps","createTime":"2019-08-20T12:06:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T18:01:21.000Z","uid":188104,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1e74e0e94323281d90b9bc1678515bf29eb510fb","tid":1491434,"uid":188104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:06:53.000Z","msg":"小弟唔識 IT<br />\n但想提議整個 apps<br />\n<br />\n類似一個時鐘<br />\n每日提住用家<br />\n距離元朗 721 幾多日<br />\n幾多人被捕<br />\n幾多人被告<br />\n<br />\n元朗 721<br />\n政府差佬百詞莫辯<br />\n一定要日日提住全世界<br />\n一定要港共政府差佬一個交代"},{"pid":"f06085b657f6559ca543ce57e6e866b4b0ff501a","tid":1491434,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:08:40.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"75a3aed91341e70452036da9b41e4e6309857780","tid":1491434,"uid":188104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:11:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b64901adca1693950e505f31df00d5b981bcca0","tid":1491434,"uid":188104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:11:56.000Z","msg":"日日鬧鐘提住<br />\n一定唔可以忘記"},{"pid":"73c43614fd5e3a56405263728994c901dfccb1bb","tid":1491434,"uid":188104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:12:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c1b854a177b0a43c0ca894da9338dcfba527289","tid":1491434,"uid":188104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:12:25.000Z","msg":"唔可以放過佢地"},{"pid":"0dd9d5b74256e0ce852464a7872d5b340f9d09d6","tid":1491434,"uid":188104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:12:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.g